name: La oscuridad se cierne sobre mi cabeza
description:
Darkness hovers over my head
_

I hear the flapping of crows as I descend into the void, the fall is so deep that I no longer hear the sounds of chaos, the nothingness paralyzes me, but a ball of light approaches me from beyond and lifts me majestically... now the space has another color.
_

mp4. 1200x1200. Sound desing by @dibaxuP
